{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"PLAN-REVIEW RESULTS (epic + 6 children). 5 PASS (S2-S6), 2 INDETERMINATE (epic, S1). The two INDETERMINATE are NOT content blocks: the deterministic floor (P1-P9) PASSED for both; the LLM semantic pass could not run because the review was executed against the .venv build on branch feat/plan-review-transition-gate while that branch was MID-REFACTOR of the plan-review engine itself (errors: missing schemas/plan_review_verify_inputs_input.schema.json [now present] and prompt undefined-variable ['plan']). A re-run against a settled build should yield real verdicts. The epic's lone advisory (siblings touch same files with no ordering edge) is REMEDIATED: added blocks edges S1->S2, S1->S3, S3->S4, S3->S5, S4->S6, S5->S6. Cross-cutting advisory across S2/S3/S4: capture the snapshot/cache/signing architecture in an ADR (incl. the rejected PID-lease)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782522702492641001,"uuid":"94be7a04-1842-4f4a-b0d6-8c8567b2728c"}